<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP Email - Project Peak</title>
    <style>
        /* Add your custom CSS styles here */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img class="logo" src="https://i.imgur.com/KyPxlAG.png" alt="Project Peak Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Your One-Time Password (OTP) for Project Peak</h2>
            <p>Dear <%= recipientName %>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for choosing Project Peak for your <%= service %> needs. To ensure the security of your account, we have generated a one-time password (OTP) for authentication purposes.</p>
            <p><strong>Your OTP is: <%= otp %></strong></p>
            <p>Please use this OTP within the next <%= timeFrame %> to complete your <%= action %>. Do not share this OTP with anyone for security reasons.</p>
            <p>If you did not initiate this action or have any concerns regarding the OTP, please contact our support team immediately at <%= supportContact %>.</p>
            <p>Thank you for trusting Project Peak. We look forward to serving you.</p>
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p><%= senderName %><br><%= senderPosition %><br>Project Peak</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
